            <td class="blob-code">        $resolver-&gt;setAllowedTypes(<span class="hljs-string">'attr'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'array'</span>);</td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="123"></td>
            <td class="blob-code">    }</td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="124"></td>
            <td class="blob-code">}</td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>There are easier ways to find out the valid options for a field - like the documentation
or the form web profiler tab. But sometimes, being able to see how an option is <em>used</em>
in these classes, might help you find the right value.</p>
<h2 id="the-label-option-versus-variable">The label Option versus Variable <a class="headerlink" href="form-options-variables#the-label-option-versus-variable" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
